 "FooDB FOOD00054 (compound presence for phytochemicals and free amino acids)"], "curation_notes": "Dominant carbon/energy source is citric acid (~5 g/100g, >90% of total acids), followed by the fermentable sugars fructose > glucose > sucrose (total ~2.5 g/100g) and secondary organic acids (malic, succinic, oxalic, lactic). Organic acids were the key FooDB omission and were added from peer-reviewed HPLC data (juice basis; whole-flesh values comparable). Nitrogen is supplied mainly as 1.1 g/100g protein plus free amino acids (asparagine/proline/serine/aspartate/glutamate dominant in citrus, unq", "curation_added": ["citric acid (5.0 g/100g - dominant carbon source, was absent)", "L-malic acid (0.58 g/100g)", "succinic acid (0.119 g/100g)", "oxalic acid (0.103 g/100g)", "lactic acid (0.061 g/100g)", "quantified individual sugars: D-glucose 0.98, D-fructose 1.09, sucrose 0.43 g/100g", "niacin/pantothenate/B6/folate/choline/vitamin E quantified from USDA", "full mineral panel quantified from USDA"], "curation_removed": [{"name": "Nickel", "reason": "non-nutritive trace contaminant, absent from USDA lemon panel; not a growth nutrient"}, {"name": "Co2+", "reason": "cobalt ion trace/contaminant; lemon has no B12 and Co is not a characterized lemon nutrient; FooDB artifact"}, {"name": "Iodine c", "reason": "non-nutritive trace element, negligible/absent in lemon flesh; FooDB placeholder"}, {"name": "Chromium", "reason": "non-nutritive trace element, absent from USDA lemon panel; FooDB noise"}, {"name": "Molybdate", "reason": "trace element not quantified for lemon; not characteristic; FooDB placeholder"}, {"name": "CO2 CO2", "reason": "metabolic/atmospheric gas, not a food nutrient; FooDB environment artifact"}, {"name": "O2 O2", "reason": "atmospheric gas, environment not food composition; FooDB artifact"}, {"name": "Nitrogen", "reason": "N2 gas, not a bioavailable nutrient of the food; FooDB artifact"}, {"name": "Fe2+ mitochondria", "reason": "subcellular-compartment/duplicate iron entry; consolidated into single 'iron' 0.60 mg"}, {"name": "Iron (Fe3+)", "reason": "redundant duplicate iron entry; consolidated into single 'iron'"}, {"name": "Pentadecanoic acid", "reason": "odd-chain C15:0 (ruminant/dairy fat marker); implausible/negligible in a plant food; FooDB noise"}, {"name": "Decanal C10H20O", "reason": "peel essential-oil volatile aldehyde; trace aroma, not a growth nutrient (food is flesh without peel)"}, {"name": "Dodecanal C12H24O", "reason": "peel essential-oil volatile aldehyde; trace aroma, not a growth nutrient"}, {"name": "Heptanal C7H14O", "reason": "volatile aldehyde; trace aroma compound, not a growth nutrient"}, {"name": "Nonanal C9H18O", "reason": "volatile aldehyde; trace aroma compound, not a growth nutrient"}, {"name": "Decanoic acid", "reason": "trace peel/oil medium-chain fatty acid; negligible in lemon flesh (total lipid 0.3 g)"}, {"name": "Dodecanoic acid", "reason": "trace peel/oil fatty acid (lauric); negligible in lemon flesh"}], "curation_confidence": "high"}, "components": [{"name": "citric acid", "bigg_metabolite": "cit", "exchange": "EX_cit_e", "lower_bound": -1000.0, "upper_bound": 1000.0, "concentration_mM": 260.3, "xref": {"reactome": "R-ALL-29654", "kegg": "C00158", "chebi": "CHEBI:132362", "kegg_drug": "D00037", "hmdb": "HMDB00094", "inchikey": "KRKNYBCHXYNGOX-UHFFFAOYSA-K", "biocyc": "META:CIT", "mnx": "MNXM1107752", "seed": "cpd00137", "metacyc": "CIT", "sabiork": "1952", "inchi": "InChI=1S/C6H8O7/c7-3(8)1-6(13,5(11)12)2-4(9)10/h13H,1-2H2,(H,7,8)(H,9,10)(H,11,12)/p-3", "formula": "C6H5O7"}, "in_biggr": true, "exchange_source": "biggr", "mapping_method": "name_alias_remap", "mapping_confidence": "inferred", "role": "organic_acid", "evidence_source": "Wang et al. 2021 (fresh lemon juice, HPLC) doi:10.3390/foods10102384 (PMC8588450); citric 51.46 g/L. Cross-checked Penniston 2008 (48-60 g/L).", "amount": "5.0 g/100g"}, {"name": "L-malic acid", "bigg_metabolite": "mal__L", "exchange": "EX_mal__L_e"